snippet.title: God of Riffs: Battle for the Metalverse - Official Update Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Smash enemies with your guitar axes as enemies don't stand a chance in this trailer for God of Riffs: Battle for the Metalverse. The free update for God of Riffs will be available on Meta and Steam on January 30, 2024.
